00:00:21.891 --> 00:00:26.171
Today I am going to show you a New Recipe
of Gujarati Traditional Snack "Khaman Dhokla".

00:00:26.171 --> 00:00:31.451
Basically Khaman Dhokla is Made from Gram
Flour but today I am not going to use Gram

00:00:31.451 --> 00:00:36.041
Flour at all.Instead of Gram Flour I am going
to use Flattened Rice or Poha.

00:00:36.041 --> 00:00:39.110
So let's take a look at the Ingredients one
by one.

00:00:39.110 --> 00:00:42.121
For the Poha Khaman Dhokla You will need.

00:00:42.121 --> 00:00:44.570
200 Grams Flattened Rice or Poha.

00:00:44.570 --> 00:00:46.610
2 Glass of Butter Milk.

00:00:46.610 --> 00:00:48.750
1 tsp of Turmeric Powder.

00:00:48.750 --> 00:00:52.991
1/2 (Half) Lemon.
and Salt to Taste.

00:00:52.991 --> 00:00:54.930
And For The Tadka Sauce you will need.

00:00:54.930 --> 00:00:56.140
4 tsp of Oil.

00:00:56.140 --> 00:00:58.960
1 tsp of Mustard Seeds.

00:00:58.960 --> 00:01:00.780
10 Curry Leaves.

00:01:00.780 --> 00:01:03.211
4 tsp of Sugar.

00:01:03.211 --> 00:01:07.761
Chili Rings of 2 Chilies.
and For the Garnishing you will need some

00:01:07.761 --> 00:01:13.291
Fresh Coriander Leaves and Tomato Ketchup.

00:01:13.291 --> 00:01:27.161
First of all put Butter Milk into the Pan
and than add Turmeric Powder and Salt.

00:01:27.161 --> 00:01:30.801
Let is cook for 2 Minutes on a Low heat.

00:01:30.801 --> 00:01:46.891
Meanwhile I am going to wash the Poha or Flattened
Rice and take this out into the Mixing Bowl.

00:01:46.891 --> 00:01:59.201
Now our Butter Milk is ready so I am going
to add this to the Poha.

00:01:59.201 --> 00:02:08.761
Mix this Well.

00:02:08.761 --> 00:02:14.541
After Mixing this very well take it out into
the Molding Plate and Press this with the

00:02:14.541 --> 00:02:25.861
Hand So it don't brake while cutting, and
give it a rest for around 20 Minutes.

00:02:25.861 --> 00:03:02.681
Now our Khaman is ready So I am going to cut
it into the Cubes.

00:03:02.681 --> 00:03:05.921
Now I am going to heat oil in a Pan.

00:03:05.921 --> 00:03:14.600
When Oil get heated add the Mustard Seeds,
Curry Leaves,Chili Rings and One Glass of

00:03:14.600 --> 00:03:23.541
Water with Lemon (Half) and Sugar.

00:03:23.541 --> 00:03:42.761
"Be careful while adding Water"
Let it cook for a minute on a medium low heat.

00:03:42.761 --> 00:04:07.041
Now our Tadka Sauce is ready So I am going
to give Tadka to the Khaman.

00:04:07.041 --> 00:04:27.431
So this is it let me Plate this Beautiful
looking very special Gujarati Snack.

00:04:27.431 --> 00:04:58.001
Garnish it with Coriander Leaves and Tomato
Ketchup.

